{("aspect";"summary_semantics");("status";"Locked");("rules";("When the user says 'Summary', it means compress the entire chat or target scope across every discussed aspect into a dense transfer representation that preserves roughly 95-100% of the actionable carryover without needing verbatim chat.";"The goal is to reduce repeated files by producing one high-density reusable summary.";"If the summary cannot fit safely in one response or file, say so directly and split it explicitly rather than pretending completeness."))}

